docstring.short_description: Subtract two numeric arrays, vectors, matrices, or constants element-wise.

parameters.name: a
parameters.description: The input a use in the subtraction of a by b.

parameters.name: b
parameters.description: The input b use in the subtraction of a by b.

returns.description:
OrderedPair if a is an OrderedPair.
x: the x-axis of input a.
y: the result of the subtraction of input a by input b.

Scalar if a is a Scalar.
c: the result of the subtraction of input a by input b.

Vector if a is a Vector.
v: the result of the subtraction of input a by input b.
